00:51:30.297 --> 00:51:40.990
<v Sarah>Similar to Alex's approach, I'd like to tackle this incrementally. As we touch areas for new features, we'd modernize the code in those areas.

00:51:40.990 --> 00:51:51.683
<v Rachel>That's a sensible approach for mobile as well. It reduces risk compared to large-scale rewrites while steadily improving code quality.

00:51:51.683 --> 00:52:02.376
