<v Rachel>Key risks are documented with mitigation strategies. Cross-team dependencies are mapped and we're establishing coordination mechanisms.

01:11:27.920 --> 01:11:38.613
<v Rachel>Communication plans are in place for internal stakeholders, customers, and the broader community. Budget requirements are documented for finance approval.

01:11:38.613 --> 01:11:49.306
