01:32:29.702 --> 01:32:40.395
<v Dan>The password reset flow is on my team's backlog. We could potentially move it up in priority if the competitive pressure warrants it.

01:32:40.395 --> 01:32:51.088
<v Rachel>Let's keep SSO in Q2 but add password reset improvement to Q1. Mike, does that address the most common sales objection?

01:32:51.088 --> 01:33:01.781
<v Mike>Yes, that would help significantly. Prospects often cite password issues as a friction point during trials.

01:33:01.781 --> 01:33:12.474
